Specialization:
 • In specialization, an entity is divided into sub-entities based on 
their characteristics. 

• Specialization is a top-down approach in which a higher-level 
entity is divided into multiple specialized lower-level entities.
======================================================================
| المصطلح        |       فكر فيه كده                |
| -------------- | --------------------------- |
| Generalization | بدمج كائنات شبه بعض في واحد كبير    | 
| Specialization | بفرّع كائن عام إلى أنواع فرعية        |
======================================================================
